{"tid":1701713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"要求全體警務人員減薪及免去醫療福利作即時懲罰","createTime":"2019-11-09T08:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T10:04:24.000Z","uid":336524,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7067f4de9fd9a616c9fc4fd437058732e0aceb0f","tid":1701713,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"所有自六月做防暴、速龍得返黎嘅ot錢要嘔一半，之後警察人工全部都要打折扣，最重要免去醫療福利。咁撚憎黑護就咪撚睇，唔該返大灣區。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於絕大部分防暴都係違規違法工作，而要逐一揪出實在太困難。因此全體受罰，一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n我相信呢個係暫時目前對班垃圾最大嘅懲罰，做得狗都係為錢先出賣尊嚴。我要你地依家錢又無尊嚴又無！"},{"pid":"367f0be44699f94b6b2d60f1e3d1461c59de0ca6","tid":1701713,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"要一齊令1111黎明行動成功 <br />\n你而家有四樣野可以做！<br />\n<br />\n第一 推呢個post上返熱門 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n<br />\n第二 幫手宣傳出去 ig/fb /WhatsApp/tg<br />\n第三 今晚幫手貼連儂牆<br />\n第四 加入返tg group <a href=\"http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=c463b630\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XknsjfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXknsjfF.jpg&h=083b2897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5HPxAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5HPxAG.jpg&h=81b4f697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7TGoHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7TGoHn.jpg&h=d606c29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enzeJHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenzeJHn.jpg&h=6f985462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBEVs83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBEVs83.jpg&h=90d9ea80&s=